INVOICE EDIT-FORM: calculate table summary

- function "calculateInvoiceTotalNet()" calculates and displays the total net value of the entire invoice
- function "calculateInvoiceTotalGross()" calculates and displays the total gross value of the entire invoice
- function "calculateTableSummary()" invoke function above functions (calculateInvoiceTotalNet() and calculateInvoiceTotalGross())

Other:
- add a call to the "showEmptyInfo()" and "calculateTableSummary()" functions at the moment of opening the edit form